Abandon the pawn
to save the commander.

18
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,640
I never expected Li Chi
to be so ruthless.

19
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,800
Now, the Great Yu

20
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,280
seems prosperous.

21
