25
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:38,680
What about you?

26
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,600
Now that your vengeance is fulfilled,

27
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,440
are you happy?

28
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:43,600
It's too fast.

29
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,280
Wouldn't it be better
now that success came quickly?

30
