Madam Xie,

34
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,800
the master is occupied
with important matters today

35
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,160
and is unable to see you.

36
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,760
What important matters?

37
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,640
He can't even see me?

38
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,360
Starting tomorrow,

39
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,000
I still have many loose ends to tie up.

40
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,120
Don't wait for me.

41
