It won't take long.

44
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,320
I won't be a bother.

45
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,760
Madam Xie,

46
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,040
please don't make things
difficult for me.

47
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,160
It's cold.

48
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,640
You should go back and rest.

49
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:12,760
Tell him

50
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,160
I'll be waiting for him in the room.

51
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,160
Lyuzhu,

52
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,440
have you seen the Preceptor?

53
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,000
No.

54
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,280
Miss,

55
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,800
did you have a fight with the Preceptor?

56
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,840
Na Jinci,

57
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,360
what do you mean by this?

58
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,520
Miss,

59
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,840
it's time to dress up.

60
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,240
We have to attend

61
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,880
Miss Jiang's memorial ceremony.

62
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:41,200
I need to retrieve Yue's
personal belongings.

63
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,360
What happened to you?

64
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,120
Today is Consort Li's memorial ceremony.

65
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,720
I knew you'd come.

66
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,160
Your Highness, you look so different.

67
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,040
I hardly recognize you.

68
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,200
Yin,

69
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,400
everything happened before was my fault.

70
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,280
I've now repented.

71
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,400
Can you...

72
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,320
Can you forgive me?

73
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,320
What are you doing?

74
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:25,760
Consort Li's death

75
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,560
must be related to my mother.

76
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,040
Now that

77
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,320
she's dead,

78
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,240
I'm here to offer prayers on her behalf.

79
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,800
I hope she finds peace

80
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,240
and ascends to a better afterlife.

81
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,440
There's no need.

82
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:45,080
Yue would never accept
such a hypocritical apology.

83
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,440
Yin.

84
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,240
Yin.

85
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,440
Yin, don't go.

86
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,840
Given our childhood bond,

87
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,960
can't we at least be honest
with each other?

88
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,960
Be honest with each other?

89
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,880
You want me to be honest?

90
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,400
Have you ever truly treated me
with sincerity?

91
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,080
You know better than anyone

92
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,320
how that bond came about.

93
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,800
Everything is just a lie.

94
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,640
I...

95
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,680
I did lie to you,

96
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:19,240
but I only wanted to be
with you forever.

97
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,680
I may have lied to you,

98
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,160
but my feelings for you were sincere.

99
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,520
But what about Na Jinci?

100
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:24,800
Sincere?

101
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,800
You've never been sincere.

102
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,840
How can you even compare to him?

103
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,520
Yin,

104
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,720
all men are the same.

105
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,760
I wronged you,

106
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,640
but do you think Na Jinci
is a good person?

107
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,440
His motives for approaching you

108
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,840
are far more sinister than mine.

109
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,560
What nonsense are you spouting now?

110
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,400
Now the Empress is dead

111
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,480
and he's eliminated many court officials
as he wished.

112
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,080
Think about it.

113
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,440
Does he still treat you the same way?

114
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:58,720
To him,

115
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,600
being with you

116
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,680
might be more unbearable than death.

117
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:07,080
Losing the position of Crown Prince
was your own doing.

118
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:09,720
Don't come to me with your madness.

119
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:10,960
Lyuzhu,

120
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,080
let's go.

121
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,400
If you don't believe me,

122
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,840
you can ask the elders in your clan.

123
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,400
Find out what really happened

124
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,000
between the Na family
and the Xie family years ago.

125
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,080
Xiao Zhi.

126
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:37,800
Madam Xie.

127
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,160
Where's Na Jinci?

128
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,240
Has he returned?

129
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,800
He's returned, hasn't he?

130
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,840
I'll find him.

131
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,640
Madam Xie.

132
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,160
The master said

133
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,160
he won't see you.

134
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,360
Won't see me?

135
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,160
What dose that mean?

136
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,920
It means he doesn't want to see you,

137
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,920
nor does he want you to find him.

138
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,360
You know

139
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,000
you won't be able to find him

140
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,400
if he doesn't want to see you.

141
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,840
What happened?

142
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,200
You must know.

143
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,560
Tell me, please.

144
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,080
If nothing else works,

145
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,960
take me to see him secretly,

146
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,680
please?

147
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,520
Madam Xie,

148
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:21,960
don't make things difficult for me.

149
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,440
Miss.

150
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,080
Madam Xie.

151
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,760
That's fine.

152
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,240
I won't trouble you.

153
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:36,760
Lyuzhu,

154
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,760
let's go home.

155
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,480
To the Xie Mansion.

156
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,120
Uncle Li.

157
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,080
Miss.

158
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,960
Why have you returned

159
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,040
in such a hurry?

160
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,640
What exactly happened

161
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,680
between the Na family
and the Xie family back then?

162
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,520
I only know a little.

163
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,360
Miss,

164
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,800
this morning,
when I was cleaning the study,

165
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,280
I found this box.

166
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,760
I've never seen it before.

167
00:10:07,220 --> 00:10:08,760
[Confession Letter]

168
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:10,880
This...

169
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,680
Do you recognize it?

170
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,000
Well...

171
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,000
Tell me!

172
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:22,240
This was written
by the late General Xie.

173
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,000
He intended to present it
to the Emperor.

174
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,960
How did it end up here?

175
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,560
Did grandfather really write this?

176
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,440
Yes.

177
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:33,950
[Confession Letter]

178
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,280
In my life,

179
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,920
I've fought in countless battles

180
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,320
and pacified the lands.

181
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,600
After decades in the military,

182
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,800
I've prided myself
on being upright and honest

183
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,320
with a clear conscience.

184
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,560
Yet

185
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,680
I committed one mistake,

186
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,120
which haunts me to this day,

187
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,840
making me unable to rest in peace.

188
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:15,240
Lord Na once met with me

189
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,360
and I believe his loyalty.

190
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:20,080
He isn't a traitor
seeking personal gain.

191
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,280
Perhaps we should ask His Majesty again

192
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:24,280
to avoid wrongfully killing the loyal.

193
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:27,320
I have a daughter

194
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,480
living in the Na household.

195
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,360
Now that the decree has been issued,

196
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,040
I have no choice

197
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:35,520
but to sacrifice her.

198
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:39,600
General, why do you hesitate?

199
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:40,880
Could it be

200
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,000
the Na family isn't the only one

201
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,640
colluding with Dafeng?

202
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,560
Duke, be careful with your words.

203
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:50,480
I advise you,

204
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,000
collusion and treason

205
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,520
have implicated many.

206
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:58,120
You've undertaken this special duty.

207
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:00,200
[Young Xie Tinghan]
If you defy the imperial decree,

208
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,320
If you defy the imperial decree,

209
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,240
the entire Xie family

210
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:07,440
and even the Xie Army

211
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:12,160
might not meet a good end.

212
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:12,760
But...

213
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:17,680
A soldier serves the Emperor.

214
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,160
General,

215
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:21,800
never forget your duty.

216
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,560
Do it.

217
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,920
That night,

218
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:36,320
the 48 members of the Na family

219
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,320
were executed without exception.

220
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,640
I've seen many battles

221
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:42,720
and taken countless lives,

222
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,680
but this incident haunts me,

223
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,640
making me restless every night.

224
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,880
I deeply regret it.

225
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:53,760
After investigating,

226
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:56,720
I learned the truth. It wasn't treason.

227
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,360
His Majesty was misled by villains.

228
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:03,200
The Empress and her father framed

229
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,480
and silenced the innocent

230
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,800
for their selfish gain.

231
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:09,720
Now I present this letter
to Your Majesty,

232
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:12,440
hoping you'll reconsider the case.

233
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,000
As I approach death,

234
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,280
my heart remains uneasy.

235
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,400
I hope one day

236
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,280
the wicked will be punished

237
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:21,640
and the innocent vindicated.

238
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:27,520
Miss,

239
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:27,920
you...

240
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,800
I'm fine, Uncle Li.

241
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,120
I just need some time alone.

242
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:06,760
I want you to live a long life

243
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:07,960
by my side,

244
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,440
watching as I send those
wretched people to hell

245
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,040
one by one.

246
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,040
What if

247
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,960
that tragedy never happened

248
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,880
when you were young?

249
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,720
What if?

250
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,120
It's not possible.

251
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,680
The tragedy back then

252
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:30,160
was caused by the Xie family.

253
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:35,400
How could I dare to ask you "what if"?

254
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,520
The marriage custom of Great Yu.

255
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,400
[Na Family Ancestral Hall]
A betrothed couple

256
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:42,840
must exchange jade pendants and hairpins

257
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,520
to symbolize a shared heart and unity

258
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,440
and a blessing for a long life together.

259
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,160
My hands

260
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:01,840
aren't worthy to adorn you
with the hairpin.

261
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:06,640
I'm sorry.

262
00:15:07,350 --> 00:15:12,060
[I hope the wicked will be punished
and the innocent vindicated.]

263
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,640
I'm sorry.

264
00:15:15,160 --> 00:15:15,960
Na Jinci,

265
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,760
I'm sorry.

266
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:23,480
♪Like the moon, waxing and waning♪

267
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:26,520
♪How could it ask more?♪

268
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:32,480
♪You and I are like a small boat
on the river♪

269
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:35,330
♪Rising and falling with the waves♪

270
00:15:35,330 --> 00:15:36,740
[Confession Letter]

271
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,160
Miss, why are you

272
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,120
in such a hurry?

273
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,760
I'm going to the Preceptor Mansion.

274
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,720
The Preceptor just sent word.

275
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:47,880
You can stay at the Xie Mansion.

276
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,280
No need to return.

277
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,240
No need to return?

278
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:52,080
What does that mean?

279
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:55,600
The Preceptor

280
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,760
sent a divorce letter.

281
00:15:57,760 --> 00:15:58,150
[Divorce Letter]

282
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:02,120
♪Speaking of love and hate♪

283
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:05,200
♪How can I distinguish them?♪

284
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:09,280
♪Longing for fate, praying sincerely♪

285
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:12,840
♪Yet the world does not acknowledge it♪

286
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:15,840
♪The night grows deep♪

287
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:18,560
♪Old dreams are stirred again♪

288
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:19,760
The bond between us

289
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,480
was founded on deceit.

290
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:23,360
Now that my vengeance is fulfilled,

291
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:24,960
there's nothing more I seek.

292
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,240
With our hearts no longer aligned,

293
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,400
we can't unify our minds.

294
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:30,080
This divorce letter

295
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,240
ends our relationship.

296
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,680
From now on, we shall each remarry,

297
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:35,120
never to dispute again.

