00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,160
[Signer: Dongfang Zui]
Our bond

299
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:39,760
is severed forever.

300
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,400
Even if it's all a lie,

301
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:44,000
I still want to ask him in person.

302
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:48,240
♪Yet it's hard to recognize each other♪

303
00:17:06,320 --> 00:17:08,510
♪The wind under the eaves♪

304
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:11,620
♪Gently taps on the wooden door♪

305
00:17:13,370 --> 00:17:15,850
♪The candle flame flickers
as I sleep soundly♪

306
00:17:16,150 --> 00:17:18,530
♪The night is at its peak♪

307
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:22,640
♪A thunderclap rolls♪

308
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:25,570
♪Stirring up old dreams again♪

309
00:17:27,710 --> 00:17:30,070
♪Thoughts linger
on the warmth of the past♪

310
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:33,500
♪The sincerity of the past♪

311
00:17:33,690 --> 00:17:36,850
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

312
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:40,120
♪But soon they cool♪

313
00:17:40,670 --> 00:17:44,360
♪I watch as you pass by♪

314
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:47,470
♪Not daring to ask♪

315
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:51,290
♪Like the moon, waxing and waning♪

316
00:17:51,290 --> 00:17:54,360
♪How could it ask more?♪

317
00:17:54,630 --> 00:17:59,550
♪You and I are like a small boat
on the river♪

318
00:17:59,810 --> 00:18:04,560
♪Rising and falling with the waves♪

319
00:18:27,470 --> 00:18:30,010
♪Speaking of love and hate♪

320
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:32,840
♪How can I distinguish them?♪

321
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:37,130
♪Longing for fate, praying sincerely♪

322
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:40,480
♪Yet the world does not acknowledge it♪

323
00:18:41,540 --> 00:18:43,900
♪The night grows deep♪

324
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:47,140
♪Old dreams are stirred again♪

325
00:18:48,910 --> 00:18:51,350
♪Yet the previous ones
are still within them♪

326
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:54,610
♪Why do they remain silent?♪

327
00:18:54,930 --> 00:18:58,030
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

328
00:18:58,410 --> 00:19:01,440
♪But soon they cool♪

329
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:05,620
♪I look, adding a few more strokes
to the word "love"♪

330
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:08,760
♪A new year's ring♪

331
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:12,390
♪The cicada's cry is close,
autumn leaves are near♪

332
00:19:12,610 --> 00:19:15,560
♪Yet it's hard to recognize each other♪

333
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:20,770
♪I sigh, why are you and I♪

334
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:25,880
♪Rising and falling,
drifting in this way?♪
